docs {
  ## Submit Sync Committee Contributions

  Publish multiple signed sync committee contribution and proofs to the beacon node. The beacon node will validate and broadcast them to the network.

  ### Request Body
  Array of signed contribution and proof objects, each containing:
  - `message`: The contribution and proof with `aggregator_index`, `contribution` (sync committee contribution), and `selection_proof`
  - `signature`: BLS signature over the contribution and proof message

  ### Response (200)
  Contributions are stored and broadcast to the network. Returns 200 on success.
}
